CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 27, 1954, pg. 13 reads: "The Glamorous Cotillion - Scenes from the third annual debutante Cotillion given by Pittsburgh AKAs..."
TitMainTitle: Group of men, and women, including back facing woman wearing light colored lace gown, holding handbag, standing on curved staircase with metal railing in Syria Mosque for the Alpha Kappa Alpha's 1954 Cotillion
